      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil a full kettle, then take your <strong>steak</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid, with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Pat your <strong>pork loin steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper and cut into large bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
