        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped pork loin </strong>to the dish and cook for 2 min or until lightly browned</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into wedges</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing it with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
